智利和阿根廷的安地斯山脈可以分為二區：{{link-en|乾安地斯|Dry Andes}}及{{link-en|濕安地斯|Wet Andes}}。乾安地斯由[[阿他加马沙漠|阿他加马沙漠]]延伸至[[馬烏萊河|馬烏萊河]]的區域，其降雨更為零星，且其溫度變化強烈。<!--The line of equilibrium may shift drastically over short periods of time, leaving a whole glacier in the [[ablation|ablation]] area or in the [[Glacier_ice_accumulation|accumulation area]].-->

在智利及阿根廷[[門多薩省|門多薩省]]的安地斯山脈，由於高度曝露在太陽光下，{{link-en|岩石冰河|rock glacier}}較大，也比一般冰河要常見<ref>Jan-Christoph Otto, Joachim Götz, Markus Keuschnig, Ingo Hartmeyer, Dario Trombotto, and Lothar Schrott (2010). Geomorphological and geophysical investigation of a complex rock glacier system - Morenas Coloradas valley (Cordon del Plata, Mendoza, Argentina)</ref>。

